- Branches with name abbr. as prefix, f.e. for John Smith: smi/fix-unsafe-code
- Commit messages should be written in a descriptive, imperative style
- Commit messages should be written according to the Conventional Commit specificiation <https://www.conventionalcommits.org/en/v1.0.0/>
- Minimum of TWO reviewers required before merging pull request into master
- Before merging pull requests, the code must be formatted according to the style guidelines
